reviewText: A long way from being classics...  The only good movie out of the bunch is the  Colony ...  normally these 4 movie collections are decent but not this one !!
Worth the price for Gattica, the other films kind of stink!
Just one real hit, GAT, others are on the horror side.
Colony is meh, the two are double meh, and Gattaca almost makes up for it. Buy used....

Gattaca fan may won't to pass on buying this item.  I failed to look up the other movies on IMDB and unfortunately assumed they would be close to the quality of Gattaca.  But where as Gattaca is rated over 7/10 the others are 5/10, 3/10, & 3/10.  Not a bad deal though if you would like, for a few extra dollars, some bad Sci-Fi to go with a classic Sci-Fi.
